    <item>
      <title>美国和菲律宾在不到两个月的时间内举行第二次海上演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/us-philippines-hold-second-sea-drills-in-less-than-two-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于与中国在争议海域的紧张局势持续，菲律宾和美国军队周三开始在南海举行第二次海上演习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/us-philippines-hold-second-sea-drills-in-less-than-two-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 09:42:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及提高物价，政府寻求增加国际货币基金组织贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/egypt-rings-in-2024-by-hiking-many-prices-with-sights-set-on-imf</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及官员通过提高一系列关键服务的价格来拉开新年的序幕，这给消费者带来了新的压力，因为政府希望增加收入，并可能扩大国际货币基金组织救助计划的规模。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/egypt-rings-in-2024-by-hiking-many-prices-with-sights-set-on-imf</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 09:40:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗暂停重新启动沙特航班，以缓和局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/iran-saudi-relations-iran-air-suspends-relaunch-of-saudi-flights</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗旗舰航空公司伊朗航空在中断八年之后暂停了重启飞往沙特阿拉伯的航班的计划，这是两国政治缓和的为数不多的具体迹象之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/iran-saudi-relations-iran-air-suspends-relaunch-of-saudi-flights</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 08:45:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国总理表示政策利率决策必须考虑经济风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/thai-pm-says-policy-rate-decisions-must-factor-in-economic-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维辛表示，泰国央行在决定货币政策时应考虑国家经济面临的风险，包括脆弱的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/thai-pm-says-policy-rate-decisions-must-factor-in-economic-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 07:09:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰呼吁在空袭后对俄罗斯实施更严厉的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/poland-calls-for-tighter-sanctions-on-russia-after-air-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰外交部长拉多斯瓦夫·西科尔斯基呼吁西方盟国加强对俄罗斯的制裁，并向基辅提供远程导弹，以应对最近的一系列空袭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/poland-calls-for-tighter-sanctions-on-russia-after-air-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 06:30:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国斥责两名以色列部长呼吁从加沙地带重新安置巴勒斯坦人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/state-department-rebukes-two-israeli-ministers-over-calls-to-move-palestinians</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府批评两名以色列部长呼吁在加沙地带以外重新安置巴勒斯坦人，这是一次罕见的公开谴责，突显了美国和以色列之间对该领土命运的分歧日益加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/state-department-rebukes-two-israeli-ministers-over-calls-to-move-palestinians</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 22:43:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯称以色列在贝鲁特袭击中杀死高级官员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/explosion-in-lebanon-s-capital-state-agency-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据巴勒斯坦激进组织称，哈马斯一名高级领导人在贝鲁特的爆炸中被以色列杀害，这引发了人们对加沙地区战争升级的新担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/explosion-in-lebanon-s-capital-state-agency-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 16:18:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡因战争、政治、预算压力而陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/netanyahu-boxed-in-by-fierce-pressure-over-war-politics-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当以色列最高法院周一晚间否决总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的司法改革法时，他的利库德集团批评法官在对哈马斯的战争期间做出的裁决，而此时民族团结至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/netanyahu-boxed-in-by-fierce-pressure-over-war-politics-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 15:40:34 GMT</pubDate>
